overview.en: IQG is a global open miner alliance chain based on blockchain, dedicated to creating a new digital asset IQGT, which has the characteristics of globalization, multi-domains, no borders, easy operation, fast circulation, and wide audience.
overview.zh: IQG是基于区块链的全球开放式矿工联盟链，致力打造一个全新的数字资产IQGT，其具备全球化、多领域、无国界、易操作、快流通、受众面广等特性。
